criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Femoral head fractures as diagnosed by X-ran and CT;

          -  Garden III, IV;

          -  An age of > 75 years;

          -  Both genders.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Fractures with spinal cord injury;

          -  Fractures with nerve injury;

          -  Refusal to sign the informed consent.
